                            <comment id="14453004" author="woodj" created="Fri, 25 Nov 2005 17:39:19 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I believe this is fixed in svn. I wrote a unit test to mimick the action of XMLReporter, and it correctly encodes the quotes. The code in question is in plexus-utils (org.codehaus.plexus.util.xml.Xpp3DomWriter). The fix appears to be in PrettyPrintXMLWriter.java, where quotes previously were not encoded for attributes.&lt;/p&gt;


</comment>
